00017 C * Purpose:    Fortran header file for HDF routines
00018 C * Contents: 
00019 C *     Tag definitions
00020 C *     Error return codes
00021 C *     Logical constants
00022 C * Remarks: This file can be included with Fortran user programs.  As a
00023 C *          general rule, don't use DFNT constants that don't include a
00024 C *          number in their name.  E.g., don't use DFNT_FLOAT, use
00025 C *          DFNT_FLOAT32 or DFNT_FLOAT64.  The DFNT constants that don't
00026 C *          include numbers are for backward compatibility only.  Also,
00027 C *          there are no current plans to support 128-bit number types.

00029 C *          equivalent constant declarations in the C include file 'hdf.h'
